    <item>
      <title>全球供应风险加剧，油价持于五个月高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，以及即将上任的特朗普政府可能实施的贸易关税，对全球供应构成威胁，油价维持在五个月高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：关税报告推动美元下跌，亚洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有消息称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的经济团队成员讨论了逐步提高关税以避免通胀飙升的方法，美国股指期货上涨，美元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信概述重振泰国股市的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国执政党事实上的领导人他信·西那瓦呼吁加强监管监督、改善公司治理并向长期股票投资者提供税收优惠，以重振人们对该国低迷的股市的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国证监会誓言努力稳定市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-s-securities-regulator-vows-efforts-to-stabilize-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高证券监管机构表示，将致力于建立稳定市场的机制，并誓言在新年开局令人失望之后，在 2025 年稳定市场预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-s-securities-regulator-vows-efforts-to-stabilize-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应链转移致中国对越南出口首次超过日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国关税迫使企业寻找新的供应商以避免征税，同时继续依赖中国制造商提供零部件，越南首次超过日本成为中国第三大出口目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
